tkey_site_title: TechTreeMoe - War of War Ships Tech Tree Moe
tkey_site_description: Integrate 艦隊收藏、戰艦少女、鋼鐵少女、碧藍航線、Victory Belles and fanworks to let tech tree being moemoe!
tkey_intro_1: There is lots of warship girls icons, choose your favorite and let your tech tree being moemoe.
tkey_intro_2: Using changeable button to find changeable item quickly
tkey_intro_3: Your choose will save though LocalStorage when press download button.
tkey_intro_4: Nation background and ship type icon isn't include in this mod.
tkey_tutorial_1: Use pull-down menu below ship image to choose ship previews.
tkey_tutorial_2: After choose, click download button on the top right to download mod.
tkey_tutorial_3: Click download button on the top right to download mod.
tkey_tutorial_4: After unzip, put gui folder into res_mods/x.x.x/ and enjoy!
